sequenceDiagram
    participant P as 支付服务
    participant B as RocketMQ Broker
    participant D as 支付数据库
    participant C as 下游消费组
    P->>B: 发送Half Message
    B-->>P: Half ACK
    P->>D: 提交支付本地事务
    P->>B: Commit/Rollback
    alt 二次确认丢失
        B->>P: 事务状态回查
        P->>D: 查询payment_id状态
        P-->>B: Commit或Rollback
    end
    B->>C: 投递PaymentSucceeded
